  "keyFeatures": [
    "Warm CI installs ~7x faster than pnpm and ~3x faster than Bun",
    "Reads and writes existing pnpm, npm, yarn, and bun lockfiles in place",
    "Global content-addressable store (BLAKE3) with reflink/hardlink sharing across projects",
    "Auto-installs before script/exec/test commands when lockfile or package.json changed",
    "Isolated node_modules layout preventing phantom dependency access",
    "Secure defaults: minimum release age, exotic transitive dep blocking, lifecycle script approval",
    "Full workspace support with catalog protocol, filters, and graph selectors",
    "Patch workflow (aube patch / patch-commit / patch-remove)",
    "JSR registry support alongside npm"
  ],
